"10:25:10" : {s: 10, a: 25, w: 10, r: "صرط", t: "صِرَٰطٍۢ", l: "صِرَٰط", lc: 45, tl: "ṣirāṭin", lb: "পথ/ রাস্তা, পন্থা",e: "(the) straight path", b: "পথের", i: "jalan", f: 19, rm: "a path which is even, wide enough and can be trodden without difficulty. A road/way/path, long sword."},
